{
  "stem": "5837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They told me they are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that's as much as-- I had no way of knowing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what I was told, that they're my parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and now, looking back at it, of course, these are the only parents I have, so they are my parents.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it really makes no difference who gave you birth, you know, after all, it's who takes care of you that makes a difference.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And basically, I'm their product.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You've discussed it with your mother?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think I really wanted to know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- everything was so confusing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I came home, and of course, basically this is where my life starts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is where my-- this is-- from this moment on, I do remember things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had a wonderful life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, my parents showered me with love.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are talking about 1948.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came back home, and they showered me with love.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember my parents-- my mother putting me to bed and singing me a lullaby.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- you know, and talking, and playing, and friends are coming over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when I was sick, I mean, I was the queen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people came and wrote me games and played with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't have, like, little friends that I played with, you know, but I remember getting a lot of attention and a lot of love.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they put me in school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went there to first grade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was a good student.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I think somewhere I do have that certificate to even prove it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And-- and about--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
